   "body" : "This PR consists in:\r\n - removes explicit event loop exit Ã¢ÂÂ event loop exits once there are no active or pending events\r\n - removes the list of bounded sockets as `evhttp` instance already holds them\r\n - calls `evhttp_free` with the event loop running\r\n - sends header `Connection: close` on active requests when shutdown was requested Ã¢ÂÂ libevent is aware if this header and closes the connection gracefully, and clients receive this header because event loop is still running.\r\n\r\nFixes #11777. Replaces #13501.",
